We have that
\begin{align*}
|\pi - 7| &=
\begin{cases}
\pi - 7 & \text{if } \pi > 7, \\
7 - \pi & \text{if } \pi < 7.
\end{cases} \\
|\pi - |\pi - 7|| &=
\begin{cases}
\pi - (\pi - 7) = 7 & \text{if } \pi > 7, \\
\pi - (7 - \pi) = 2\pi - 7 & \text{if } \pi < 7.
\end{cases}
\end{align*}Therefore, $|\pi - |\pi - 7|| = \boxed{2\pi - 7}$, since $\pi < 7.$

